Prediction markets covered in the NYT podcast “Hard Fork”Published on October 13, 2023 6:43 PM GMT<br/><br/><br/><br/> <a href="https://www.lesswrong.com/posts/ADkyxynJaaykteLRt/prediction-markets-covered-in-the-nyt-podcast-hard-fork#comments">讨论</a>; https://www.lesswrong.com/posts/ADkyxynJaaykteLRt/prediction-markets-covered-in-the-nyt-podcast-hard-fork ADkyxynJaayktelLRtAustin Chen Fri, 13 Oct 2023 18:43:29 GMT 
[Paper] All's Fair In Love And Love: Copy Suppression in GPT-2 SmallPublished on October 13, 2023 6:32 PM GMT<br/><br/><p><i>这是 Callum McDougall、Arthur Conmy 和 Cody Rushing 所做工作的随附博客文章，作为 SERI MATS 2023 的一部分。这项工作由 Neel Nanda 和 Tom McGrath 指导。您可以在 https://arxiv.org/abs/2310.04625 找到我们的全文</i><a href="https://arxiv.org/abs/2310.04625."><i>。</i></a><i>我们 i) 总结我们的主要成果，ii) 讨论局限性和未来的工作，iii) 列出从该项目中吸取的经验教训</i></p><h1>主要结果</h1><h2>复制抑制</h2><p>在论文中，我们将<strong>复制抑制</strong>定义为以下算法：</p><blockquote><p>如果较早层中的组件预测某个标记，并且该标记在上下文中出现较早，则注意力头会抑制它。</p></blockquote><p>我们表明，GPT2-Small 中的注意力头 L10H7（以及较小程度上的 L11H10）都<strong>在整个分布中执行复制抑制，并且该算法解释了它们 76.9% 的行为</strong>。</p><p>例如，以<i>“爱情和战争中一切都是公平的”这句话为例。</i>如果我们消融 L10H7，模型将错误地预测<i>“……爱和爱”。</i>这个过程的示意图： </p><figure class="image image_resized" style="width:73.36%"><img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/ebezsHW6qJwxTFasX/oss906vqmfsmpk8gugcf" srcset="https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/ebezsHW6qJwxTFasX/ittzvyhneoxhqgmxudx4 140w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/ebezsHW6qJwxTFasX/eix0mq6jga7kee01d0gq 280w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/ebezsHW6qJwxTFasX/c5z7umw5u6qm4gzx8in6 420w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/ebezsHW6qJwxTFasX/s9bpw2zjqx0g3ykyhqmk 560w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/ebezsHW6qJwxTFasX/f9dnerexqib9sm93rkai 700w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/ebezsHW6qJwxTFasX/dqmeoyj9gey6rjawktp0 840w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/ebezsHW6qJwxTFasX/jjm8nhzonaq9ijwbp89l 980w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/ebezsHW6qJwxTFasX/fbxwnufume261qrsdrfk 1120w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/ebezsHW6qJwxTFasX/by2rma3wem8xpm1ghbjl 1260w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/ebezsHW6qJwxTFasX/f7u2ce8fc7razlv8xhzp 1322w"></figure><p>还有几个例子： </p><figure class="image"><img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/ebezsHW6qJwxTFasX/pketju5qapelbxlczoo9" srcset="https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/ebezsHW6qJwxTFasX/ukoizgutckbxymn4w6xl 140w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/ebezsHW6qJwxTFasX/plddjbypqjn6inslvrwa 280w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/ebezsHW6qJwxTFasX/iygedqfsguvlwcddebn2 420w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/ebezsHW6qJwxTFasX/m8mfotoip6oelqxy1lcf 560w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/ebezsHW6qJwxTFasX/l67hy20n9scap4pfzyzp 700w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/ebezsHW6qJwxTFasX/l2s898ukrmrljhyvkmzf 840w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/ebezsHW6qJwxTFasX/lctgz1fodm38igs4slye 980w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/ebezsHW6qJwxTFasX/ufcphicfkoorrsfpndvg 1120w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/ebezsHW6qJwxTFasX/y28kuqju0ur22niqrmiu 1260w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/ebezsHW6qJwxTFasX/batzrhwh8p4cadunjau6 1360w"></figure><h2>复制抑制-保留消融</h2><p>为了测试我们解释了多少 L10H7 的行为，我们设计了一种称为<strong>复制抑制保留消融 (CSPA)</strong>的消融形式。这个想法是，CSPA 应该删除头部的所有功能<i>，除了</i>复制抑制之外。如果这完全破坏了性能，那么磁头就不会进行复制抑制；如果它根本不影响性能。</p><p> CSPA 的技术细节可以在我们的论文中找到。 CSPA 非常宽松地做了两件重要的事情：</p><ul><li>删除从源令