</style><span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="S"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.519em; padding-bottom: 0.298em; padding-right: 0.032em;">S</span></span></span></span></span></span></span> <span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label=""><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"></span></span></span></span></span>到目标令牌<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="D"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">D</span></span></span></span></span></span></span> ，除了在头 L10H7 之前的<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="D"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">D</span></span></span></span></span></span></span>处预测令牌<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="S"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.519em; padding-bottom: 0.298em; padding-right: 0.032em;">S</span></span></span></span></span></span></span>的那些。</li><li>对于未删除的信息，将其投影到令牌<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="S"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.519em; padding-bottom: 0.298em; padding-right: 0.032em;">S</span></span></span></span></span></span></span>的非嵌入中（并丢弃正分量），因此我们仅捕获抑制我们正在关注的令牌的直接效果。</li></ul><p><strong>本文的主要结果如下图所示</strong>。 <span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="D_{CSPA}"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-msubsup"><span class="mjx-base"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">DC</span></span></span> <span class="mjx-sub" style="font-size: 70.7%; vertical-align: -0.241em; padding-right: 0.071em;"><span class="mjx-texatom" style=""><span class="mjx-mrow"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.519em; padding-bottom: 0.298em; padding-right: 0.045em;">S</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.519em; padding-bottom: 0.298em; padding-right: 0.032em;">P</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em; padding-right: 0.109em;">A</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.519em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">是</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>（应用 CSPA 后的预测）和（原始预测）之间的 KL 散度。 <span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="D_{MA}"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-msubsup"><span class="mjx-base"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">D</span></span></span> <span class="mjx-sub" style="font-size: 70.7%; vertical-align: -0.241em; padding-right: 0.071em;"><span class="mjx-texatom" style=""><span class="mjx-mrow"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em; padding-right: 0.081em;">M</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.519em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">A</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>是（均值消融后的预测）和（原始预测）之间的 KL 散度。每个点都是一堆这些值的平均值（我们<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="D_{MA}"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-msubsup"><span class="mjx-sub" style="font-size: 70.7%; vertical-align: -0.241em; padding-right: 0.071em;"><span class="mjx-texatom" style=""><span class="mjx-mrow"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.519em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">根据</span></span><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em; padding-right: 0.081em;">DMA</span></span></span></span></span> <span class="mjx-base"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">的</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>值进行分组）。换句话说，该图上的每个 (x, y) 点代表一组点的（来自平均消融的平均 KL div，来自 CSPA 的平均 KL div）。该线非常接近 x 轴，表明复制抑制很好地描述了该头正在执行的操作。 </p><figure class="image image_resized" style="width:57.34%"><img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/ebezsHW6qJwxTFasX/bnlk0eru69tjis3e2i1v" srcset="https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/ebezsHW6qJwxTFasX/o2jt58vdm60rlpon98pk 100w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/ebezsHW6qJwxTFasX/bz9vyk4pbjmwxts3fjha 200w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/ebezsHW6qJwxTFasX/mobq0zuck4ihzaeepws8 300w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/ebezsHW6qJwxTFasX/l7oajun9qrzvvf5vg3je 400w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/ebezsHW6qJwxTFasX/voap7dowe7fgujylhq5j 500w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/ebezsHW6qJwxTFasX/oucsnggwpltxg59vhcts 600w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/ebezsHW6qJwxTFasX/bhs3jslnlfcisxviqyzc 700w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/ebezsHW6qJwxTFasX/kg11skiq26sajyxmwoex 800w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/ebezsHW6qJwxTFasX/mth9lw9en7p6dljjepps 900w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/ebezsHW6qJwxTFasX/m9a7jrsqwhf1a7zavjve 982w"></figure><h2>抗感应</h2><p>Anthropic 的论文<a href="https://transformer-circuits.pub/2022/in-context-learning-and-induction-heads/index.html">In-context Learning and Induction Heads</a>观察到<strong>反归纳头</strong>的存在，它似乎关注重复的前缀，但<i>抑制</i>后缀而不是增强它。例如，在提示<code>Barack Obama ... Barack</code>中，他们会关注<code>Obama</code>令牌并<i>减少</i>分配给下一个令牌是<code>Obama</code>概率。这对我们来说听起来很像复制抑制，因此我们将反归纳分数与复制抑制分数（通过 IOI 任务中间接对象标记被抑制的程度来衡量）进行了比较，我们发现象限中存在很强的相关性，其中两个分数均为正值： </p><figure class="image"><img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/ebezsHW6qJwxTFasX/p0uqo1htadvgctjuixye" srcset="https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/ebezsHW6qJwxTFasX/dcdqkoxp2wduia3loy4e 170w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/ebezsHW6qJwxTFasX/icd2bpf0mnkwue5ffjxq 340w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/ebezsHW6qJwxTFasX/jfm12hz5abeqivlw3qel 510w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/ebezsHW6qJwxTFasX/jvzk9lkrcfg002p4rmjp 680w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/ebezsHW6qJwxTFasX/ktxe05dhzjwjp4kfagsu 850w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/ebezsHW6qJwxTFasX/hkb4hhijlqkopbgvqvwz 1020w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/ebezsHW6qJwxTFasX/pkplikxhovawaxbq4ndz 1190w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/ebezsHW6qJwxTFasX/zalpvpnpsr4wgrahlond 1360w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/ebezsHW6qJwxTFasX/hu116tkzga5zko19l3nw 1530w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/ebezsHW6qJwxTFasX/b0ob33n0esi48196qqfe 1667w"></figure><p>这特别有趣，因为它展示了模型组件如何在特定分布中产生重要影响，尽管没有任何特定于任务的知识。 <i>“关注并抑制当前预测令牌的先前实例”</i>的一般复制抑制算法似乎对我们在上图中观察到的特定于分布的行为负责。</p><h2>语义相似度</h2><p>另一个很酷的发现：模型知道标记何时具有“语义相似性”。预测的标记 (T) 不必与关注的标记相同；它们可能因大写/复数/动词时态/前置空格等而有所不同。嵌入向量余弦相似度并不能完全解释这一点 - 语义相似的单词比余弦相似度所暗示的复制抑制更多。 </p><p><img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/ebezsHW6qJwxTFasX/suiucjncv65qagocsvh9" srcset="https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/ebezsHW6qJwxTFasX/zcounotzprc1kht3vb1a 190w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/ebezsHW6qJwxTFasX/z9tjaan8yzwqxox6fhoc 380w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/ebezsHW6qJwxTFasX/vohthwlpfabdnukuuao4 570w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/ebezsHW6qJwxTFasX/s6ummo8ijhc6ggnpfvh8 760w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/ebezsHW6qJwxTFasX/gbzunkuv6p13tnjs7gd3 950w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/ebezsHW6qJwxTFasX/tntwcpwuggyl4fcjp3dl 1140w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/ebezsHW6qJwxTFasX/j76tch9pgaebrnch5q2g 1330w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/ebezsHW6qJwxTFasX/bzjuenegi3xkzzovbplr 1520w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/ebezsHW6qJwxTFasX/ruhdiuwddxmrpimolw53 1710w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/ebezsHW6qJwxTFasX/mwz5yy7tybqpugl2fgy7 1807w"></p><h2>自我修复</h2><p>事实证明，复制抑制是模型如何进行<a href="https://arxiv.org/abs/2307.15771">自我修复</a>的重要组成部分，在这种现象中，消融组件会导致后续组件<i>在同一前向传递中</i>补偿消融。使用<a href="https://arxiv.org/abs/2211.00593">间接对象识别</a>（IOI）任务作为案例，我们强调当您消除复制时，没有什么可以复制抑制：自我修复！这有助于解开原始 IOI 论文中首次引入的负头自我修复之谜。 </p><figure class="image"><img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/ebezsHW6qJwxTFasX/s5jthcspm1u6rwigttoi" srcset="https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/ebezsHW6qJwxTFasX/ioutv2hblx07oygeisoa 130w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/ebezsHW6qJwxTFasX/nyobxejn9phvd2vpt6vp 260w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/ebezsHW6qJwxTFasX/qa9bwqjvnpgva9y4q9fx 390w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/ebezsHW6qJwxTFasX/leahjwipy24azl0swdph 520w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/ebezsHW6qJwxTFasX/lfuk1brebtzanhnjduzx 650w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/ebezsHW6qJwxTFasX/ykerquoxdigdopxyfgnl 780w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/ebezsHW6qJwxTFasX/np9ftddip0j2y9pky4wo 910w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/ebezsHW6qJwxTFasX/el9v5szltoebwcwakhl6 1040w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/ebezsHW6qJwxTFasX/gfftottzmefbzvhd4deg 1170w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/ebezsHW6qJwxTFasX/trus2brk2upwfaiyomep 1204w"><figcaption>我们发现不同性质的自我修复形式</figcaption></figure><p>我们进行了一些实验来展示复制抑制如何解释 IOI 任务中发生的部分（但不是全部）自我修复。我们还使用 Q-Composition 在基于权重的水平上发现这一点。不过，我们留下的问题比开始时要多得多，并且对未来更多研究自我修复的工作感到兴奋！ </p><figure class="image image_resized" style="width:54.15%"><img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/ebezsHW6qJwxTFasX/qq5tcbkg9i7nny0u12vv" srcset="https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/ebezsHW6qJwxTFasX/xhpfpnqfdmjqa5ntuzia 144w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/ebezsHW6qJwxTFasX/lkvl4isnxadlw8ti8rvx 224w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/ebezsHW6qJwxTFasX/qowikbfnkbm3t6syvnxy 304w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/ebezsHW6qJwxTFasX/itge7tuugn5qy2l0726r 384w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/ebezsHW6qJwxTFasX/lvms4kvk3u2zswzykt8j 464w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/ebezsHW6qJwxTFasX/pu6siwxqhl7fwbbncpt2 544w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/ebezsHW6qJwxTFasX/leto6gxrabgqgjh2jyb3 624w"><figcaption>我们发现名称移动器头和自我修复头之间基于权重的关系：红色边缘表示较少，蓝色边缘表示较多，由于名称移动器头而对名称的关注</figcaption></figure><h2>互动网页</h2><p>我们还创建了交互式可视化来配合本文。您可以在我们的<a href="https://copy-suppression.streamlit.app/">Streamlit 应用程序</a>上看到它们。该应用程序使您能够执行以下操作：</p><ul><li>浏览 OpenWebText 示例提示，并查看（基于每个令牌）：<ul><li>烧蚀头 L10H7 改变了损失和最高预测令牌多少，</li><li> L10H7 最关注哪些代币，</li><li> L10H7 哪个代币增强/抑制最多。</li></ul></li><li>分析注意力头 L10H7 的权重，看看当关注特定标记时哪些标记受到最大程度的抑制，</li><li> ...以及其他一些功能。 </li></ul><figure class="image image_resized" style="width:94.38%"><img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/ebezsHW6qJwxTFasX/xfwkdvzpjaryetmfmp0h" srcset="https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/ebezsHW6qJwxTFasX/wskhjplqviob6tymbczx 120w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/ebezsHW6qJwxTFasX/c11oshxvdloxbaumuzcj 240w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/